query:
SELECT 
  t.id,
  t.userId,
  t.accountId,
  t.ticket,
  t.symbol,
  u.email as user_email,
  ta.accountNumber
FROM trades t
LEFT JOIN users u ON t.userId = u.id
LEFT JOIN trading_accounts ta ON t.accountId = ta.id
ORDER BY t.createdAt DESC
LIMIT 5;
